{"type": "article", "id": 25578, "title": "表情，就是我们在聊天时候的人格", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 1317, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>出于羞涩，和“为了在三次元世界让人喜欢”，我们的真人状态难免都会……不太过火。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152752iqaH5t4KMvn18BZo.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55307263\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>但这并不能代表我们澎湃的内心戏！并不能！</p>\n<p>在对着屏幕聊天这件事情上，光是文字和感叹号早已不能表达我们真实的人格。自拍的，会动的，反应表情和心情的绚烂图片才是正道！</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152753L1uPS9mgjhMvGQnc.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634375\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>也只有在这个时候才觉得自己比较有趣了。</p>\n<p>表情就和衣柜里面的衣服一样，永远都少一个。</p>\n<p>所以……动手来制作吧！</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152754FNyt2GI6sAUTgQJ0.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n\n\n"}